<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>11350</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>16024</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不好了！”史密斯侦探说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>16025</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>20142</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那只怪物会毁了美罗城的会展中心。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>20143</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>25336</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我们必须......火箭女孩儿？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>25337</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>30871</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西落在了美罗城会展中心门前。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>30872</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>33568</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>大楼的屋顶不见了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>33569</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>38572</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>到处都是破碎的玻璃和砖头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>38573</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>42318</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>人们正往大楼外面跑。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>42319</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>47317</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“怪物吃了我的花！”一个男人喊道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>47318</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>52963</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“快逃命啊！”一个抱着空花盆的女人大喊道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>52964</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>59303</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>嗷！大地震动起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>59304</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>64800</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一道影子遮住了会展中心。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>64801</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>69753</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一只巨大的怪物站在大楼后面。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>69754</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>77385</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>怪物有一条长尾巴，身上还有绿色的鳞片。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>77386</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>82135</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>看起来像一只巨型爬行动物。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>82136</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>85416</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西咽了一口口水。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>85417</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>91316</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“怪物比我想象中的更大。”嗷！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>91317</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>99653</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>怪物把爪子伸向会展中心，掏出一把玫瑰，吃掉了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>99654</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>110402</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>怪物打了一个大饱嗝，然后转身离开了会展中心。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>110403</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>119902</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>怪物用鼻子闻了闻花园里的花，然后把它们都拔掉了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>119903</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>123902</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>它继续往前走。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>123903</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>127404</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我得阻止它！”罗西说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>127405</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>131653</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“它正往玛拉家所在的小区走呢！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>131654</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>134651</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西快速追向怪物。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>134652</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>139401</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>嗞！罗西的眼睛里发射出激光，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>139402</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>143653</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是激光又被怪物反弹了回来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>143654</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>149401</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>怪物转过身来。嗷！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>149402</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>153652</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>怪物把罗西拍进了屋顶。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>153653</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>159402</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>怪物继续往前走。一边闻，一边吃花。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>159403</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>166402</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>在玛拉家的后院里，杰克、特勒尔和玛拉抬头向上看。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>166403</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>169653</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哇！”杰克叫道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>169654</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>174653</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“好大一只怪物！”特勒尔叫道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>174654</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>178654</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西飞在怪物后面。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>178655</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>182151</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我眼睛激光不管用。”她想，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>182152</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>184655</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我要想个别的办法。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>184656</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>191901</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她发现了一个大水箱，举起来快速飞向怪物。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>191902</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>196687</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你们看！”玛拉叫道，“火箭女孩儿！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>196688</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>202142</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西把水箱砸向怪物。水箱破了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>202143</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>209738</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>水泼在玛拉、杰克和特勒尔身上。嗷！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>209739</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>214734</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“坏了！”罗西想，“怪物现在生气了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>214735</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>219982</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>怪物跑向罗西，想要再一次打她。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>219983</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>224317</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西躲开了。“哈！”罗西说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>224318</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>227067</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你打不到我......啊！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>227068</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>232179</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>怪物扬起了大尾巴，把罗西打出了很远。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>232180</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>236383</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西砰的一声掉到了城市另一边。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>236384</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>240047</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西快速飞回玛拉的小区。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>240048</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>243610</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>怪物正在往山那边走。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>243611</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>248772</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>咚！咚！咚！山在晃动。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>248773</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>252954</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一块巨大的石头掉下来，向山下滚去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>252955</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>255324</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>又一块石头掉下来了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>255325</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>258341</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>接着，另一块也掉下来了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>258342</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>263268</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>很快，很多石头都快速地向山下滚去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>263269</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>266380</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>山下有很多大楼。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>266381</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>269435</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“坏了！”罗西叫道，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>269436</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>274686</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这些石头会毁了美罗城的！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>